body:
GPUs on MacOS are not supported by us anymore, until apple and nvidia start fully supporting this setup.
In the meantime, here is a duplicate.
https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/issues/9072

Please feel free to contribute fixes if you can get the build to work, I will be happy to review and merge the changes.
